t;:&quot;138&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"3\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"4\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"5\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-active\" style=\"width: 138px;\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n                \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            5\/5 - (8 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131;\">GIA S\u01af TI\u1ebeNG ANH &#8211; CHUY\u00caN NG\u1eee, PH\u00c1T \u00c2M CHU\u1ea8N &#8211; CH\u1eaeC NG\u1eee PH\u00c1P T\u1ea0I H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Hotline: 0962.005.996 &#8211; 0987.005.996<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Trung T\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u <strong>gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/strong> gi\u1ecfi d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea1y online trong m\u00f9a d\u1ecbch:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfng anh t\u1eeb m\u1ea7m non, ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, Thcs, Thpt, \u00f4n thi chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p, \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Luy\u1ec7n thi ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 IELTS, TOEIC, TOEF, SAT, ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfng anh A-B-C<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Ti\u1ebfng anh giao ti\u1ebfp, h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt, luy\u1ec7n ph\u00e1t \u00e2m, luy\u1ec7n 4 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><b>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">H\u1ecdc online 1 k\u00e8m 1 ho\u1eb7c 1 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 1 nh\u00f3m nh\u1ecf h\u1ecdc sinh ( T\u1eeb 2-5 b\u1ea1n) qua c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Zoom, Google Meet, Zalo, Skype&#8230;.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">D\u1ea1y k\u00e8m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp 1 k\u00e8m 1 ho\u1eb7c nh\u00f3m (h\u1ecdc nh\u00f3m t\u1eeb 2-5 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao)<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">H\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">L\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc, th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">Th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc: T\u00f9y v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc trong kho\u1ea3ng 1,5 &#8211; 2h\/bu\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1471\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1471\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1471\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-gia-su-la-gi-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-gia-su-la-gi-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-gia-su-la-gi-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-gia-su-la-gi-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-gia-su-la-gi.png 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1471\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>H\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc 1 k\u00e8m 1 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_6_LOI_ICH_CUA_HOC_GIA_SU_TIENG_ANH_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>I &#8211; 6 L\u1ee2I \u00cdCH C\u1ee6A H\u1eccC GIA S\u01af TI\u1ebeNG ANH T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m ti\u1ebfng anh<\/strong> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, t\u01b0 duy c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 05 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><em>Gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9, hi\u1ec3u b\u00e0i<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><em>C\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc sinh<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><em>H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i h\u1ecdc trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 100k &#8211; 150k\/bu\u1ed5i<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><em>Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edd gi\u1ea5c c\u1ee7a con.<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><em>Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian \u0111i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a cha m\u1eb9, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf giao th\u00f4ng.<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 v\u1eeba l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y, v\u1eeba l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n t\u00e2m giao v\u1edbi con<\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p3\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><em>==&gt;&gt; <strong>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u00ed do tr\u00ean, gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a cha m\u1eb9 gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n.<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem ngay:<\/strong> 3000+ <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-500-gia-su-mon-toan-gioi-tu-lop-1-12-o-ha-noi\/\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n<\/strong><\/a><\/span> gi\u1ecfi, chuy\u00ean To\u00e1n, chuy\u00ean s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m, d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1-12 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/strong> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-500-gia-su-vat-ly-gia-su-su-pham-gioi\/\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n L\u00fd<\/strong><\/a><\/span> &#8211; Th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng cha m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 h\u1ecdc cho con m\u00f4n L\u00fd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_TIENG_ANH_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>II &#8211; H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af TI\u1ebeNG ANH T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i style=\"color: #555555;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><h2 id=\"tablepress-33-name\" class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-33\">H\u1eccC PH\u00cd - GIA S\u01af TI\u1ebeNG ANH<\/h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-33\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-33 tbody-has-connected-cells\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-33-name\">\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"column-1\">L\u1edaP H\u1eccC<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n\t<td class=\"column-2\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 1<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">120.000 \u2013 150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">150.000 \u2013 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 \u2013 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">L\u1edbp 6,7,8<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">130.000 \u2013 150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">180.000 \u2013 200.00<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 \u2013 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">L\u1edbp 9<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 350.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 - 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 3<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">220.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 350.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000 - 400.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">180.000 - 220.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">220.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">300.000 - 350.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-8\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, HS chuy\u00ean<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-33 from cache --><\/span><br \/>\n&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i>\u00a0 \u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tham kh\u1ea3o. H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi chi ti\u1ebft xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7\u00a0<span style=\"\">0962.005.996<\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><strong>&gt;&gt;Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong> B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 <\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\">h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0<\/a><\/span><span style=\"color: #282828;\"> c\u00e1c m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c: To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, Ho\u00e1, V\u0103n, N\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu&#8230;. \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem ngay:<\/strong> TOP 300+ <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-gia-su-luyen-chu-dep-tai-nha-tien-bo-chi-sau-1-thang\/\">gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/a><span style=\"color: #000000;\">,\u00a0<\/span><\/span>ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p ch\u1ec9 sau 1 kho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_NEN_THUE_GIA_SU_LA_SINH_VIEN_HAY_GIAO_VIEN\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>III &#8211; N\u00caN THU\u00ca GIA S\u01af L\u00c0 SINH VI\u00caN HAY GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean hay gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o 1 s\u1ed1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">???? <strong>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kinh t\u1ebf gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/strong>: H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi sinh vi\u00ean t\u1eeb 100.000 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1eeb 220.000.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">???? <strong>H\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a con<\/strong>: N\u1ebfu con h\u1ecdc qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m, m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp chung, cha m\u1eb9 n\u00ean thu\u00ea gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m con. N\u1ebfu con h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c h\u1ecdc, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap con h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">???? <strong>Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0<\/strong>: Nh\u1eefng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 \u00f4n thi chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea5p, \u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, cha m\u1eb9 n\u00ean thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_962\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-962\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-962\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/1-1.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-962\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #282828;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t ( t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng )<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_GIA_SU_DAY_TIENG_ANH_TAI_NHA\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>IV &#8211;\u00a0CAM K\u1ebeT GIA S\u01af D\u1ea0Y TI\u1ebeNG ANH T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd ki\u1ec3m tra ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecdc sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\">Bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, <strong>gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y ti\u1ebfng anh<\/strong> s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0i test ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c cho h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a em. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc th\u1eed v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng anh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">V\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t, gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed (Bao g\u1ed3m: 1 bu\u1ed5i test ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c &amp; 1 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh ), n\u1ebfu sau 2 bu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd thu\u00ea gia s\u01b0 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia s\u01b0 n\u00e0y th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u1ee5 huynh. T\u1ea1i gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t, ph\u00ed t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, t\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><strong>\u2705\u00a0Ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m tra l\u00fd l\u1ecbch gia s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">M\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a <strong>gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh h\u00e0 n\u1ed9i<\/strong> bao g\u1ed3m s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00ed l\u1ecbch v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng khai v\u1edbi ph\u1ee5 huynh. Khi qua gia \u0111\u00ecnh d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc, sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh th\u1ebb cho ph\u1ee5 huynh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1479\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1479\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1479\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-thu-750x340-300x136.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1479\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><em>H\u1ecdc th\u1eed 02 bu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 Ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; V\u1edbi 9 n\u0103m trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01a1n 5000+ gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n gi\u1ecfi, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; G\u1ecdi ngay Hotline: <span style=\"\">0962.005.996<\/span> ho\u1eb7c <span style=\"\">0987.005.996<\/span> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a con b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #282828;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 100%;\">Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top1-gia-su-van-ha-noi-bang-gia-mon-van-moi-nhat-2018\/\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 V\u0103n<\/strong><\/a><\/span> t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 cho con &#8211; C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 sau 01 th\u00e1ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; N\u1ebfu anh ch\u1ecb c\u00f2n ch\u00e1u nh\u1ecf \u0111ang h\u1ecdc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u201c B\u00ed k\u00edp ch\u1ecdn <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/\"><strong>gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/a> <\/span>chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c m\u1eb9 chia s\u1ebb \u201c<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt; <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-gia-su-hoa-gioi-o-ha-noi-tu-lop-8-12-chi-tu-100k\/\">Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n Ho\u00e1<\/a><\/span><\/strong> &#8211; <span style=\"color: #000000;\">Xo\u00e1 b\u1ecf n\u1ed7i lo m\u00e0 7\/10 h\u1ecdc sinh s\u1ee3 h\u1ecdc HO\u00c1<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p7\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #d83131;\"><strong>TRUNG T\u00c2M\u00a0GIA S\u01af\u00a0TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 1: N03, S\u1ed1 38-40 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 2: S\u1ed1 263 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, ph\u01b0\u1eddng Xu\u00e2n H\u00f2a, t\u1ec9nh Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd, Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 3: 479 L\u0129nh Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Mai, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p2\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><b>==&gt; Hotline (24\/7): 0962.005.996 \u2013 0987.005.996<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GIA S\u01af TI\u1ebeNG ANH &#8211; CHUY\u00caN NG\u1eee, PH\u00c1T \u00c2M CHU\u1ea8N &#8211; CH\u1eaeC NG\u1eee PH\u00c1P T\u1ea0I H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3465,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[492],"tags":[446,447],"class_list":["post-3270","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gia-su-tieng-anh-mb","tag-gia-su-day-tieng-anh-tai-nha","tag-gia-su-day-tieng-anh-tai-nha-ha-noi"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>[Top 1] Gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh H\u00e0 - Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p, Ph\u00e1t \u00e2m chu\u1ea9n<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y Ti\u1ebfng Anh t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng S\u01b0 Ph\u1ea1m, Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef, Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng.... D\u1ea1y th\u1eed 2 bu\u1ed5i cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-tieng-anh\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"C\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y tr\u1ebb t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 - \u0110\u1ec3 con \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0T\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd \u0111ang b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb em. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh lo l\u1eafng c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 con t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9. Nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y tr\u1ebb t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. B\u1eb1ng k\u1ecbnh ngh\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 quan s\u00e1t th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u1ee3i \u00fd c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y tr\u1ebb b\u1ecb t\u1ef1 k\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 huynh tham kh\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1y con \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-tieng-anh\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2020-08-18T11:46:05+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2021-09-08T15:49:09+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Foto-ni\u00f1o.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"600\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"320\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/